FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c].[Id], [c].[UserId]
    FROM [Carts] AS [c]

) AS [t]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c].[Id], [c].[UserId]
    FROM [Carts] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[UserId] = @__userId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [CartDetails] AS [c0] ON [t].[Id] = [c0].[CartId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [c0].[CartId]

SET IMPLICIT_TRANSACTIONS OFF;
SET NOCOUNT ON;
UPDATE [CartDetails] SET [Quantity] = @p0
OUTPUT 1

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[UserId], [c0].[CartId], [c0].[ProductId], [c0].[Price], [c0].[Quantity]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c].[Id], [c].[UserId]
    FROM [Carts] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[UserId] = @__userId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [CartDetails] AS [c0] ON [t].[Id] = [c0].[CartId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [c0].[CartId]
2023-11-01 11:37:10.452 +07:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[@p1='?' (DbType = Int32), @p2='?' (DbType = Int32), @p0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SET IMPLICIT_TRANSACTIONS OFF;
SET NOCOUNT ON;
UPDATE [CartDetails] SET [Quantity] = @p0
OUTPUT 1
WHERE [CartId] = @p1 AND [ProductId] = @p2;
